\frac{\partial V_{\text {ref }}}{\partial T}=(m-1) \frac{k}{q} \ln \left(\frac{T_{0}}{T}\right) \tag{7.27}
\end{equation*}
$$

These equations can be used to estimate the temperature dependence at temperatures differing from the reference temperature. In the subsequent section, a practical bipolar implementation of a bandgap reference will be discussed.

#### EXAMPLE 7.4

